*Kombi* je stara ali udobna vozila. (The *combine* is an old but comfortable vehicle.)

On je često vozio svoj *kombi*. (He often drove his *combine*.)

Ona je putovala *kombijem*. (She travelled by *combine*.)

*Kombi*-autobusi su bili popularni tokom 1970-ih. (*Combine*-buses were popular during the 1970s.)

Ona je često išla u grad *kombijem*. (She often went to the city by *combine*.)